 we are using a Dell Unity system. Apologies if this is a basic question—while my background is in networking, I have enough storage knowledge to be cautious.</p>','',576,260,'2024-10-18 17:42:15',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(51,29,'members','last_activity','','','',0,NULL,'2024-10-18 20:06:08',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(52,29,'bbpress','bbp_reply_create','','<p>A great question. MPIO functions effectively only across different Layer 2 subnets. You can add as many subnets as needed or consider upgrading your network to higher speeds. Rest assured, there will be no risk of traffic blackholing.</p>','',577,576,'2024-10-18 18:01:16',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(53,30,'members','last_activity','','','',0,NULL,'2024-10-20 18:26:53',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(54,14,'bbpress','bbp_reply_create','','<p>First paragraph 1</p><p>First paragraph 2</p>','',634,576,'2024-11-07 16:32:46',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(55,25,'members','new_member','','','',0,0,'2024-11-13 16:01:02',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(56,25,'members','last_activity','','','',0,NULL,'2024-11-14 21:35:06',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(57,25,'bbpress','bbp_topic_create','','<p>I found that Cloud based SSDs are 15x more expensive than on-premises servers. Is it worth the move?</p>','',647,553,'2024-11-14 20:19:17',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(58,25,'bbpress','bbp_topic_create','','<p>Which is the best performing SAN for mid sized organizations in the market?</p>','',648,553,'2024-11-14 20:19:45',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(59,25,'bbpress','bbp_topic_create','','<p>Huawei OceanStor Dorado versus Dell EMC PowerMax? Which is better?</p>','',649,553,'2024-11-14 20:20:34',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(60,25,'bbpress','bbp_topic_create','','<p>Fiber channel versus iSCSI which one to use?</p>','',650,553,'2024-11-14 20:21:33',0,0,0,0,'public','published'),(61,25,'bbpress','bbp_topic_create','','<p>What storage system is better suited for a few billion small files (of around 16K)?</p>','',651,553,