INSERT INTO `wp_bp_groups` VALUES (1,3,'Security','security','The information era is characterized by the transition to cloud computing, mobile Internet, Big Data, and virtual networks. How can you find a security solution that is uniquely qualified to provide comprehensive protection for the information era?','public',0,0,'2024-07-20 04:18:59'),(2,7,'Artificial Intelligence','artificial-intelligence','Artificial intelligence (AI) is a wide-ranging branch of computer science that aims to build machines capable of performing tasks that typically require human intelligence. While AI is an interdisciplinary science with multiple approaches, advancements in machine learning and deep learning, in particular, are creating a paradigm shift in virtually every industry.','public',0,0,'2024-07-13 06:31:20'),(3,2,'Servers','servers','Discussion forum for a wide range of high-performance servers, including rack servers, blade servers, and high-density servers. Each product specializes in different elements of the IT environment but all deliver reliable, cost-effective and high-performance computing.','public',0,0,'2024-07-15 11:50:00'),(4,12,'Storage','storage','All discussions about the process of using technology to preserve digital information for later use and retrieval. It allows computers and other devices to store and access data in a structured way, which makes data management and processing easier.','public',0,0,'2024-07-12 13:32:52'),(5,6,'Cloud & Big Data','cloud-bigdata','Discussion forum on cloud computing solutions for enterprises. The cloud and big data gives enterprises and service providers agile, on-demand IT services on a variety of cloud types, including private, hybrid, desktop, video, and all-in-one cloud platforms.','public',0,1,'2024-07-04 01:32:23'),(6,12,'Routing & Switching','routing-switching','CloudEngine, Campus, and SMB Switches combine advanced architecture and design with carrier-grade reliability to provide high-availability, high-performance networking for large-scale data centers, ISPs, and enterprise IT networks.','public',0,0,'2024-07-14 01:51:58'),(7,6,'Innovation Club','innovation-club','Innovation is truly a confusing buzzword which many people love to hate. Every business leader agrees that it is important. But nobody can quite seem to agree on what it actually is or what it means.','public',0,0,'2024-07-15 19:27:13'),(8,9,'Backup & Recovery','backup-recovery','Backup and recovery is the process of making copies of data and storing them in a safe place in case of loss or damage. When needed, the data can be restored to its original location or a safe alternative so it can be used again.','public',0,0,'2024-07-09 06:45:57');
