e guardian or from the minor\\u2019s unsupervised use are irrelevant to the community.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>2.3 If a user uses an inappropriate nickname and avatar, the community reserves the right to disqualify the user.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>2.4 Users are obligated to keep their passwords and accounts secure. If any loss of credentials occurs (either inside the community and\\/or within a third party) that is caused by the inappropriate custody of the account and password, the user shall compensate the loss suffered by the community and\\/or the third party and eliminate the impacts.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>2.5 If the user does not use the account more than one year after registration, the community reserves the right to freeze their account.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>2.6 If the user finds that their account has been used without authorization or if any abnormal situation occurs, the user shall modify the account password and store it properly. If the account is illegally used due to hacker behavior or negligence of the user\\u2019s custody, the community does not bear the responsibility.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>2.7 After receiving the notification that the user requests the community to take measures to suspend the login and use of their account due to abnormal behaviors, the community has the right to ask the user to provide and verify the valid personal identify information consistent with the registered identify information. If the information provided is consistent with the registered identity information, the community shall take measures in time to suspend the login and use of the account. If the user does not provide the valid personal identity information or the valid personal identity information provided by the user is inconsistent with the registered identity information, the community has the right to reject the foregoing requirements of the user.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3. <strong>User community rules<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.1 Users have the right to raise any questions or express their opinions in their posts or comments in the community in compliance with the code of conduct herein.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.2 When creating a reward post, users have the right to set the reward amount and set the best answer among the valid replies made by other users.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.3 Users can gain bonus points according to the bonus point rules of the community or by participating in activities. Users can exchange bonus points for gifts in the Rewards section.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.4 Users are entitled to user level upgrades and badges based on their contributions to the community.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.5 When using the community, users shall comply with all the applicable laws, regulations, and policies of the related countries or regions.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.6 By using the community, users agree to abide by the following rules:<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list {\\\"ordered\\\":true} -->\\n<ol class=\\\"wp-block-list\\\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Comply with all network agreements, regulations, and procedures related to the network services;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not use the community for any behavior that may adversely affect the normal operation of the Internet;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not use the community to transmit any explicit information, including but not limited to harassment, slander, abuse, intimidation, or in a manner that infringes any intellectual property rights of any kind;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not post content that is deemed valueless and irrelevant to the community. Non-technical discussions and unauthorized reposting are not allowed in the community, including the following:<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul class=\\\"wp-block-list\\\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>creating non-technical discussion posts, including but not limited to enormous discussions on entertainment, gossip, and valueless content that falls out of or beyond the scope of technology;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>unauthorized reposting, including but not limited to reposting a post that is not annotated with the source or of which reposting is not expressly permitted.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list --><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not interfere or attempt to interfere in the normal operation of any function of the community;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not avoid, try to avoid, or claim to avoid the content protection mechanisms or data metric tools built in the community;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Do not use the community in any way to infringe Huawei\'s commercial interests, including but not limited to placing commercial advertisements that are not permitted by the community.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ol>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>3.7 Users shall not use the community to disseminate sensitive information that violates applicable laws and policies, including but not limited to the following kinds of information:<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul class=\\\"wp-block-list\\\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Containing the content prohibited by laws and administrative regulations.<\